06:50.106 --> 06:52.106
<i> This is not the
country we fought for.</i>

06:52.141 --> 06:54.341
We were fighting for a future

06:54.376 --> 06:57.544
where there is a peace,
there is a stability,

06:57.580 --> 06:59.279
there is prosperity.

06:59.315 --> 07:02.083
So, indeed, people are upset

07:02.118 --> 07:05.652
<i>about where we have found
ourselves in the country.</i>

