the ousted vice president.

07:30.578 --> 07:32.245
<i>They concluded
that at the root</i>

07:32.280 --> 07:34.280
<i>of the power struggle
is a fierce battle</i>

07:34.315 --> 07:36.482
<i>over control
of the state's assets.</i>

07:36.517 --> 07:39.318
<i>They're stealing the
money to fund their militias,</i>

07:39.354 --> 07:41.888
to attack and kill one another.

07:41.923 --> 07:44.223
<i>South Sudan's leaders
