07:44.259 --> 07:45.958
<i>were getting rich
off lucrative deals</i>

07:45.993 --> 07:47.960
<i>in the oil and mining industries</i>

07:47.995 --> 07:52.164
<i>while the country was driven
into war and famine.</i>

07:52.199 --> 07:55.434
<i>Fourteen-year-old Bol is among
the nearly two million people</i>

07:55.470 --> 07:57.069
<i>who were forced from their homes</i>

07:57.104 --> 07:59.337
<i>and now scattered
