08:00.207 --> 08:01.539
How did you get here?

08:14.889 --> 08:16.621
Do you think
about your family a lot?

08:25.965 --> 08:27.599
<i>To find out
how the ongoing war</i>

08:27.634 --> 08:29.967
<i>is affecting civilians
outside of Juba,</i>

08:30.003 --> 08:32.535
<i>we flew north,
crossing ethnic lines</i>

08:32.571 --> 08:34.738
<i>to the tribal home
of the opposition.</i>

08:35.842 --> 08:38.876
<i>More than 120,000 ethnic Nuers</i>

08:38.912 --> 08:42.346
<i>are now living inside
this one barbed-wire camp.</i>

08:42.381 --> 08:46.050
<i>UN peacekeepers protect them
